"<pad> LSTM performs well even with a beam size of 1, and a beam of size 2 provides most of the benefits of beamsearch. by reversing the source sentences, the LSTM\u2019s test perplexity dropped from 5.8 to 4.7. LSTMs trained on reversed source sentences did much better on long sentences than LSTMs4trained on raw source sentences. LSTMs trained on raw source sentences performed better on short sentences than LSTMs4trained on raw . a </s>"